title: Void: No. Nine (Project Vinland)
description:
You can find chapters for Vinland Saga by Makoto Yukimura translated by scanlation group Project Vinland here.

Synopsis: 300 years ago, God destroyed the old world and killed humans, leaving only the "emissaries". But underground humans live in the tunnel-filled Reform City. They search for relics, while living in fear from the threat of being hunted by the "emissaries".
author: Shima Shinya
